cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158182/', '', 'Amoxapine, Viloxazine', 'Protriptyline, Viloxazine', 1767369485);
