 effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158197/', '', 'Duloxetine, Vilazodone, Sertraline, Paroxetine, Desvenlafaxine, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, More', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 1767369485);
